{
  "doc_id": "51233",
  "text": "In order to find an optimal choice for the conservation filter in PACCMIT we used the proteomics dataset reported by Baek et al. [CITATION_1] . This dataset covers three highly conserved miRNAs. For the sake of statistical analysis, an arbitrary classification of the miRNA-gene pairs between functional and non-functional was performed based on the log 2 fold changes (log 2 FC) in protein expression, with the same cutoff as in other studies [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Specifically, miRNA-gene pairs with log 2 FC#20.2 were labeled as functional targets while the remaining pairs were labeled as non-functional targets.",
